== 地位認可 ==
其他頂尖球員，包括[[大衛·費雷爾|大衛·費雷爾]]、[[托馬什·伯蒂奇|托馬什·伯蒂奇]]、[[特松加|特松加]]、以及[[安迪·羅迪克|安迪·羅迪克]]等球員曾經均表示過四巨頭對球壇的統治讓他們在面對四人的時候都有很大的挑戰。<ref>[http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-01-24/tsonga-unsure-how-to-end-27big-four27-dominance/4481518 "Tsonga unsure how to end 'big four' dominance". ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-01-24/tsonga-unsure-how-to-end-27big-four27-dominance/4481518 |date=20201129125858 }}ABC. 24 January 2013. {{英文}}</ref><ref>[http://sports.ndtv.com/australian-open-2013/news/202232-david-ferrer-reluctant-to-claim-big-four-status "David Ferrer reluctant to claim 'Big Four' status". ] {{Wayback|url=http://sports.ndtv.com/australian-open-2013/news/202232-david-ferrer-reluctant-to-claim-big-four-status |date=20150922001758 }}NDTV Sports. 20 January 2013.{{英文}}</ref><ref>[http://www.worldtennismagazine.com/archives/6220 "By The Numbers: Dominance Of The 'Big Four'".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.worldtennismagazine.com/archives/6220 |date=20201112001508 }} World Tennis Magazine. 23 January 2012.{{英文}}</ref>費雷爾曾經說過：
{{cquote|在我個人的觀點裡，我認為四巨頭是非常優秀的。但我在每一場比賽中都嘗試著去打敗他們。但結果往往是非人所願。在他們面前似乎不能做到什麽。因為他們，我很難在大滿貫中拿到冠軍，從這點來說，他們確實强於其他球員。|大衛·費雷爾}}

很多已經退役的球員，包括[[比約恩·博里|比約恩·博里]]、[[安德烈·阿加西|安德烈·阿加西]]、[[皮特·桑普拉斯|皮特·桑普拉斯]]、[[戈蘭·伊萬尼塞維奇|戈蘭·伊萬尼塞維奇]]等在這個觀點中也表達了他們的個人想法。 <ref>[http://www.australianopen.com/en_AU/news/articles/2013-01-25/201301251359113526065.html  "Andre's back". ] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029200854/http://www.australianopen.com/en_AU/news/articles/2013-01-25/201301251359113526065.html |date=2013-10-29 }}Australian Open. 25 January 2013.{{英文}}</ref><ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/tennis/australianopen/9826014/Australian-Open-2013-Federer-Nadal-Djokovic-Murray-this-is-golden-era-of-mens-tennis-says-Andre-Agassi.html  "Australian Open 2013: Federer, Nadal, Djokovic, Murray – this is golden era of men's tennis, says Andre Agassi". ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/tennis/australianopen/9826014/Australian-Open-2013-Federer-Nadal-Djokovic-Murray-this-is-golden-era-of-mens-tennis-says-Andre-Agassi.html |date=20201111192740 }}Telegraph. 25 January 2012.{{英文}}</ref><ref>[http://sports.espn.go.com/sports/tennis/wimbledon11/columns/story?columnist=ubha_ravi&id=6671956  Wimbledon: Pete Sampras' take on the big four ] {{Wayback|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/sports/tennis/wimbledon11/columns/story?columnist=ubha_ravi&id=6671956 |date=20131030022046 }} ESPN {{英文}}</ref><ref>[http://www.nbcsports.com/id/50583671/ns/sports-tennis/  "Bridging Gap to 'Big Four' Proving Too Tough for Rest".]{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} Reuters. 25 January 2013.{{英文}}</ref><ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/tennis/wimbledon/8577949/Wimbledon-2011-Andy-Murray-is-playing-in-the-golden-age-of-tennis-for-the-mens-game-says-Bjorn-Borg.html  "Wimbledon 2011: Andy Murray is playing in the golden age of tennis for the men's game, says Bjorn Borg". ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/tennis/wimbledon/8577949/Wimbledon-2011-Andy-Murray-is-playing-in-the-golden-age-of-tennis-for-the-mens-game-says-Bjorn-Borg.html |date=20201101024039 }}Telegraph. 16 June 2011. {{英文}}</ref>在[[2011年溫布頓網球錦標賽男子單打比賽|2011年溫布頓網球錦標賽]]比賽期間，11屆大滿貫冠軍得主比約恩·博里表示：

