=== 其他觀點  ===
==== 「三巨頭」  ====
{{main|網壇三巨頭}}
有些網球評論員，甚至於穆雷本身<ref>[http://www.tennis.com/pro-game/2012/12/murray-not-there-yet-big-3/45767/#.UQqh47_ZaSo  "Murray: Not there yet with Big 3". ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tennis.com/pro-game/2012/12/murray-not-there-yet-big-3/45767/#.UQqh47_ZaSo |date=20200729093156 }}Tennis.com. Retrieved 31 January 2013. {{英文}}</ref>都曾把現今男子網壇形容為“三巨頭”或是“三國鼎立”的局面<ref>[http://bleacherreport.com/articles/757402-roger-federer-rafael-nadal-novak-djokovic-a-trivalry-in-mens-tennis Roger Federer, Rafael Nadal, Novak Djokovic: A Trivalry in Men's Tennis ] {{Wayback|url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/757402-roger-federer-rafael-nadal-novak-djokovic-a-trivalry-in-mens-tennis |date=20131030002552 }}By
Marcus Chin(Correspondent) on July 4, 2011{{英文}}</ref>，認為以穆雷的實力更應該排在其他三巨頭之後<ref>[http://sports.yahoo.com/news/dominance-big-three-good-tennis-fans-thoughts-203700608--ten.html  "Is the Dominance of the Big Three Good for Tennis?: Fan's Thoughts".] {{Wayback|url=http://sports.yahoo.com/news/dominance-big-three-good-tennis-fans-thoughts-203700608--ten.html |date=20131029212416 }} Yahoo! Sport. Retrieved 31 January 2013. {{英文}}</ref><ref>[http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/tennis/story/2012-06-21/wimbledon-novak-djokovic-rafael-nadal-roger-federer/55743598/1 "When will anyone, besides Big 3, win a major?".] {{Wayback|url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/tennis/story/2012-06-21/wimbledon-novak-djokovic-rafael-nadal-roger-federer/55743598/1 |date=20140221065651 }} USA Today. Retrieved 31 January 2013.{{英文}}</ref>，但又優於第二梯度的球員的位置。穆雷對戰其他三巨頭的成績是較不理想的29勝56敗。從2008年9月到2013年1月，穆雷是四巨頭裏面唯一一個曾經掉出世界前四的球員。但從2008年到2013年之間，穆雷拿到了九個大師賽的冠軍，2011年到2012年連續五個大滿貫四強，2012年倫敦奧運會金牌得主，2012年到2013年四次進入大滿貫決賽，最後成功摘得2012年美網及2013年溫網冠軍。媒體及評論員認為，以這樣的斐然成績并名列世界第二的成績，已足以讓穆雷成為四巨頭的一份子。<ref>[http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2012/sep/11/andy-murray-us-open-press-review "Andy Murray's US Open win, press review: 'The Big Three is the Big Four'". ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2012/sep/11/andy-murray-us-open-press-review |date=20200727000836 }}The Guardian. Retrieved 31 January 2013. {{英文}}</ref><ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/tennis/andymurray/9539568/Andy-Murrays-grand-slam-victory-gives-Big-Four-extra-strength-in-fight-for-more-prize-money.html "Andy Murray's grand slam victory gives 'Big Four' extra strength in fight for more prize money".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/tennis/andymurray/9539568/Andy-Murrays-grand-slam-victory-gives-Big-Four-extra-strength-in-fight-for-more-prize-money.html |date=20190831162844 }} Daily Telegraph. Retrieved 31 January 2013. {{英文}}</ref>
之後在2016年澳網、法網得到亞軍，拿下溫網冠軍、奧運金牌和年終賽冠軍，終於成功在2016年登上世界第一，才讓許多人認同莫瑞為四巨頭之一。<ref>[http://www.tennis.com/pro-game/2016/11/andy-murray-novak-djokovic-no-1-atp-world-tour-finals-london/62530/ "Andy Murray beat Novak Djokovic and clinched No. 1 in true Big-4 style".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tennis.com/pro-game/2016/11/andy-murray-novak-djokovic-no-1-atp-world-tour-finals-london/62530/ |date=20200726224247 }} Tennis.com. Retrieved 20 November 2016. {{英文}}</ref>
